nodes.text: A resistance group fought the Galactic Empire on a backwater planet. Ryenne considered them to be enthusiastic but overmatched. The Rebel Alliance partnered with them in 0 ABY to raid the Imperial communications hub on Sunfall Peak.
Two Imperial-class Star Destroyers were more Imperial firepower than they had ever seen.
The resistance group appears in the opening short story of the Star Wars: Age of Rebellion Core Rulebook released by Fantasy Flight Games in 2014.
